	<!-- Heavy Automatic Shotgun "Abzats" -->
    <ThingDef ParentName="BaseGun_LongBarreled">
        <defName>PaWT_Abzats</defName>
        <label>Abzats HAS</label>
        <description>The Heavy Automatic Shotgun, or "Abzats", is a makeshift Shotgun, It resembles (and is derived from) a cut-down DShK 12.7mm machine gun, re-chambered and re-bored for shotgun shells, and completely redesigned to be wielded by one user. The weapon itself had problems. Like its machine gun parent, it is very heavy, weighing more than twenty pounds despite steps taken to reduce its weight.</description>
